---
// Fundations
import Text from "@/components/fundations/elements/Text.astro";
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="bg-[#111110] scroll-mt-24">
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-32">

    <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
      <p class="text-xs font-sans font-normal uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-500 mb-6">
        About
      </p>
      <Text tag="h2" variant="displayMD" class="text-[#f0ede8] font-display leading-snug">
        We're a boutique firm built around one belief: the best design thinking is strategic, and the best AI strategy is designed.
      </Text>
      <Text tag="p" variant="textLG" class="font-sans font-normal text-[#a8a89f] leading-relaxed mt-8">
        Ruth Design Co. is an AI strategy and product design consultancy. We work with founders, operators, and leadership teams who are building something real — and who need a senior partner who can think at the strategic level and execute at the product level. We're small by design. Every engagement is led by a principal, not handed to a junior team.
      </Text>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-white/[0.08] mt-16 pt-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-24 items-start">

        <div class="md:col-span-2" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
          <div class="w-full aspect-[4/5] bg-[#1a1a18] border border-white/[0.08] rounded overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/Tyler.png" alt="Tyler Burton, Founder & Principal of Ruth Design Co." class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
          <Text tag="h3" variant="displaySM" class="font-display text-[#f0ede8] leading-snug">
            Tyler Burton, Founder & Principal
          </Text>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
            <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="font-sans font-light text-[#a8a89f] leading-relaxed">
              Tyler brings 12 years of product design experience across creative agencies, enterprise product organizations, and management consulting — with a track record of embedding in complex, high-stakes environments and delivering systems that actually ship.
            </Text>
            <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="font-sans font-light text-[#a8a89f] leading-relaxed">
              Before founding Ruth Design Co., he spent two years as a consultant with McKinsey & Company, where he learned to diagnose business problems before proposing design solutions. His McKinsey engagements spanned regulated industries and capital-intensive operations — including a generative AI tool for a major mining operation that was unanimously approved by its board and moved into engineering within the engagement timeline.
            </Text>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="font-sans font-light text-[#a8a89f] leading-relaxed">
          He went on to lead product design at Walmart, where he helped establish the AI pattern library and governance frameworks now used by teams across the company — one of the largest AI deployments in enterprise retail. Earlier in his career, he designed digital products for the NFL, Apple Music, Meta, and Sony, and led UX strategy for Medtronic's surgical planning platform alongside a global McKinsey team.
        </Text>
        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="font-sans font-light text-[#a8a89f] leading-relaxed">
          He founded Ruth Design Co. to bring that combination — consulting rigor, enterprise-grade design execution, and hands-on AI building capability — to the companies that need it most but rarely have access to it.
        </Text>
      </div>
    </div>

  </Wrapper>
</section>
